 characters interact with the environment are all factors the player must consider when approaching gameplay and competition. Characters will be designed and balanced to suit different environments and strategies.</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Unique Characters:</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Players will have the choice of picking from an array of different characters, all of whom vary in terms of weapon type, movement options, and how they interact with the environment around them.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","developers":["Randy Sabella","Tony Mangione","Sean Griffiths","Spyros Dimitropoulos","Guillaume Riviere","Eric Weiss"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154390/header.jpg?t=1737059753","is_free":false,"legal_notice":"Copyright VHornet 2025\u00a9","linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257074692,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257074692/movie480.mp4?t=1737059752","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257074692/movie_max.mp4?t=1737059752"},"name":"Neon Knights Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257074692/33064d85e278ae66cb3c6f213685a816b59ae458/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1737059752","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257074692/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1737059752","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257074692/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1737059752"}}],"name":"Neon Knights","package_groups":[],"pc_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>